data.description:
Extradentary Avon Crest home, many updates, roof, siding, windows, gutter covers, doors, electric, bathrooms. Harwood floors through out, amazing Sunroom off the kitchen, fabulous family room, great entertainment center. Den/Office, perfect for a quiet office work space. A lovely inground pool, summer paradise, new pump, safety cover, fenced in separately from the rest of the yard. The basket ball court, added fun in an already spacious park like backyard setting. Niskayuna schools, short drive to route 7, convenient to the Capital District!
Home warranty included!
